•   h.(n+1)

=   Definition of h

    ( n :: ↓( p : 0 ≤ p ≤ n : f.p.n ) ).(n+1)

=   λ comp

    ↓( p : 0 ≤ p ≤ n+1 : f.p.(n+1) )

=   Split-off term

    ↓( p : 0 ≤ p ≤ n : f.p.(n+1) ) ↓ f.(n+1).(n+1)

=   Theory [1], with p:= n+1

    ↓( p : 0 ≤ p ≤ n : f.p.(n+1) ) ↓ 1

=   Theory [5]

    ↓( p : 0 ≤ p ≤ n : f.p.n * a.n ) ↓ 1

■

